general_notes: The participant 78CFD was initially scared of the vaccine, but got it after her son's dad got very sick with COVID. She did not get the booster because she felt that COVID was not as big of a deal anymore. She was also getting pressure at work to get the booster. She is now concerned that COVID tests are no longer free.
